						<summary>

						<p>This inscription registers the construction of the shrine, with steps besides the images of Subrahmaṇya Piḷḷaiyār, Deivānaiyār and Vaḷḷināchchiyār which were installed by Tiruvāṉayār Aḻagar, a native of Kalavaiyūr in Sundarachōḻapuram.</p>						

